Class MockContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • lambda.context.MockContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.amazonaws.services.lambda.runtime.Context
    public class MockContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.amazonaws.services.lambda.runtime.Context

    Represents a Lambda execution environment by implementing the Context interface.

    This object helps enabled contemporary TDD practices while developing AWS Lambda functions.

    Methods returning primitive types may leverage environment level dependency injection.

    Methods returning complex types may depend on subsequent default DI or set custom values.
